5.0 release of CloudSim brings:
 * cleaning of meta-information of the repository
 * various fixes in code logic, including:
    * determining of date of next event in simulation
    * mapping allocating of PEs to VMs
    * computing of date of end of migration
    * destroying all VMs
    * and more
 * improving interface for the computation of power consumption of a host
 * replace custom logging system with SLF4J
 * reorganize repository structure and Maven build process